<br>
Betrayer of friends, she couldn't bring herself to aspire to.<br>
<br>
As she left the arena, she looked back at the berserk Iksar once more....</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Goodbye Gore.  I'm sorry I failed you.<br>
